OOC: The Quintessons had control of the Terrorcons in a transformer
episode, and I thought it would be fitting if he came with them.

BIC:
Rippersnapper looks at Cutthroat, "Hunt goooood, we hunt" he screamed, and
flew towards the bush, where he saw the mech fluid, "Target, fresh" he
screams, and transforms into his monster mode. He smells the fluid, and
runs into the forest.

Wildrider realises that if they find Condor, they will most likely kill
him. "Ohhhh no, Motormaster is gonna be pissed".
